Fig. 9 is a plan view partially showing a folded state of the airbag shown in Fig. 8;
Figs. 10 and 11 are cross-sectional views of a fixation portion of an airbag apparatus according to another embodiment of the present invention in which second attachment portions are different from those in the foregoing embodiments;
