Fig. 13 is a plan view showing a folded state of the airbag shown in Fig. 12; and
Figs. 14 and 15 are a cross-sectional side view and a cross-sectional front view each showing a state in which the airbag shown in Fig. 12 is accommodated in a vehicle ceiling.
